The paper proposes a new data model for electronic medical records (EMRs) and constructs a dataset based on this model. The paper focuses on the semantic definitions of medical entities, events, and temporal relations, which are important concepts in clinical research. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the database (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories.
